{"article_id":"3gVyY8ro8azxkOmc","edus":[{"id":0,"text":"WASHINGTON -","depth":1},{"id":1,"text":"While Wisconsin struggles to hold its primary on Tuesday ,","depth":6},{"id":2,"text":"President Donald Trump and Democrats are bickering over how to provide voters with safe and secure access to a ballot","depth":7},{"id":3,"text":"as the coronavirus pandemic rages in the U.S.","depth":8},{"id":4,"text":"and threatens to extend into the fall ,","depth":9},{"id":5,"text":"affecting the general election .","depth":9},{"id":6,"text":"With another economic rescue package in the works , House Speaker Nancy Pelosi says","depth":8},{"id":7,"text":"she wants money","depth":8},{"id":8,"text":"to give more voters the chance","depth":8},{"id":9,"text":"to cast their ballot by mail , an option","depth":9},{"id":10,"text":"that would allow people to vote","depth":10},{"id":11,"text":"without the concern over the safety of polling places .","depth":10},{"id":12,"text":"But Trump opposes voting by mail","depth":7},{"id":13,"text":"and is leading Republicans in a battle","depth":9},{"id":14,"text":"to limit its use ,","depth":9},{"id":15,"text":"arguing","depth":9},{"id":16,"text":"that it would encourage fraud","depth":10},{"id":17,"text":"and lead to so many people voting","depth":11},{"id":18,"text":"that his party could not win .","depth":11},{"id":19,"text":"But the 2020 presidential election is creeping ever closer ,","depth":7},{"id":20,"text":"and there are no signs yet of the pandemic abating ,","depth":8},{"id":21,"text":"nor any word on when Americans on orders","depth":10},{"id":22,"text":"to stay home","depth":10},{"id":23,"text":"can resume normal life ,","depth":9},{"id":24,"text":"so lawmakers are trying to figure out how to allow for voting in a world","depth":7},{"id":25,"text":"where face-to-face contact causes anxiety at the least and possibly sickness and death .","depth":7},{"id":26,"text":"The debate is playing out now in Wisconsin .","depth":7},{"id":27,"text":"It stands apart from other states","depth":10},{"id":28,"text":"that have delayed primaries","depth":11},{"id":29,"text":"because of the virus ,","depth":11},{"id":30,"text":"though Democratic Gov . Tony Evers has issued a statewide stay-at-home order .","depth":9},{"id":31,"text":"Evers initially joined Republican leaders","depth":10},{"id":32,"text":"in seeking to hold the primary","depth":11},{"id":33,"text":"as planned on Tuesday ,","depth":11},{"id":34,"text":"but he now favors an all-mail election with absentee voting well into May .","depth":9},{"id":35,"text":"Republicans maintain","depth":8},{"id":36,"text":"that in-person voting should go on","depth":9},{"id":37,"text":"as planned","depth":9},{"id":38,"text":"and have asked the U.S. Supreme Court to block extended absentee voting .","depth":7},{"id":39,"text":"The election features the Democratic presidential primary between Joe Biden and Bernie Sanders ,","depth":6},{"id":40,"text":"but a bigger concern for Republicans is a state Supreme Court race","depth":7},{"id":41,"text":"that pits a conservative incumbent against a liberal challenger .","depth":7},{"id":42,"text":"In recent weeks ,","depth":7},{"id":43,"text":"as Democrats nationwide have argued","depth":8},{"id":44,"text":"the country must prepare for voting largely by mail ,","depth":8},{"id":45,"text":"Republicans have objected to or blocked expansions of such voting in Arizona , Georgia and Pennsylvania .","depth":6},{"id":46,"text":"\" It shouldn ' t be mail-in voting .","depth":7},{"id":47,"text":"It should be","depth":8},{"id":48,"text":"you go to a booth","depth":9},{"id":49,"text":"and you proudly display yourself , \"","depth":9},{"id":50,"text":"Trump told reporters Friday evening .","depth":6},{"id":51,"text":"Earlier this week on Fox News Channel ' s \" Fox & Friends , \" he claimed","depth":6},{"id":52,"text":"the Democrats had a plan","depth":7},{"id":53,"text":"\" that","depth":8},{"id":54,"text":"if you ever agreed to it","depth":9},{"id":55,"text":"you ' d never have a Republican elected in this country again . \"","depth":9},{"id":56,"text":"More than 290,000 people in the United States have tested positive for the virus so far ,","depth":6},{"id":57,"text":"prompting more than a dozen states to delay their presidential primaries .","depth":6},{"id":58,"text":"Health officials are warning","depth":7},{"id":59,"text":"that the virus has the potential","depth":8},{"id":60,"text":"to return with a second wave during the next flu season ,","depth":8},{"id":61,"text":"putting voters and poll workers in a dilemma","depth":7},{"id":62,"text":"where fulfilling a civic duty means putting their health at greater risk .","depth":7},{"id":63,"text":"Colorado , Hawaii , Oregon and Washington already provide registered voters with a ballot in the mail for all their elections ,","depth":9},{"id":64,"text":"according to a Congressional Research Service report .","depth":9},{"id":65,"text":"California and Utah are among the states","depth":9},{"id":66,"text":"that give counties the option of mail-in voting .","depth":9},{"id":67,"text":"Proponents say","depth":10},{"id":68,"text":"it can improve participation , particularly with voters","depth":11},{"id":69,"text":"who have to work on election day ,","depth":12},{"id":70,"text":"go to school","depth":13},{"id":71,"text":"or have mobility issues , such as the elderly or the sick .","depth":13},{"id":72,"text":"It could reduce the number of poll workers","depth":11},{"id":73,"text":"needed ,","depth":11},{"id":74,"text":"as well as the long lines","depth":11},{"id":75,"text":"that often arise during a presidential election .","depth":11},{"id":76,"text":"\" It just makes us more democratic , \"","depth":11},{"id":77,"text":"Pelosi told reporters this week .","depth":11},{"id":78,"text":"\" It just gives more people the opportunity","depth":11},{"id":79,"text":"to vote .","depth":11},{"id":80,"text":"So that is something","depth":10},{"id":81,"text":"we would like to see . \"","depth":10},{"id":82,"text":"Trump contends","depth":8},{"id":83,"text":"fraud would increase with more mail-in voting ,","depth":8},{"id":84,"text":"declaring ,","depth":8},{"id":85,"text":"\" I think","depth":9},{"id":86,"text":"a lot of people cheat . \"","depth":9},{"id":87,"text":"A North Carolina congressional election had to be rerun last year","depth":7},{"id":88,"text":"because the Republican candidate ' s campaign had engaged in widespread fraud through mail ballots .","depth":7},{"id":89,"text":"But some Republicans have come to embrace the format ,","depth":9},{"id":90,"text":"arguing","depth":10},{"id":91,"text":"it can be done securely","depth":11},{"id":92,"text":"and is cheaper and fairer than in-person elections .","depth":11},{"id":93,"text":"Utah , a GOP stronghold , is a recent convert to mail-in voting .","depth":8},{"id":94,"text":"Evidence shows","depth":9},{"id":95,"text":"it is Republicans , rather than Democrats , who are most likely to vote by mail ,","depth":9},{"id":96,"text":"said Michael McDonald , a University of Florida professor","depth":9},{"id":97,"text":"who tracks balloting .","depth":9},{"id":98,"text":"State and local governments are responsible","depth":5},{"id":99,"text":"for determining whether or how to offer mail-in voting .","depth":5},{"id":100,"text":"A few bills","depth":7},{"id":101,"text":"introduced during the current session of Congress","depth":7},{"id":102,"text":"would require states to allow for early or mail-in voting for federal elections .","depth":6},{"id":103,"text":"Others would require states to allow mail-in voting during national emergencies","depth":7},{"id":104,"text":"and authorize the funds","depth":8},{"id":105,"text":"to help defray the costs .","depth":8},{"id":106,"text":"The $ 2.2 trillion rescue package","depth":10},{"id":107,"text":"that Congress passed","depth":10},{"id":108,"text":"included $ 400 million for states","depth":9},{"id":109,"text":"to invest in the next election","depth":9},{"id":110,"text":"so they could expand early voting ,","depth":10},{"id":111,"text":"move to mail-in voting ,","depth":11},{"id":112,"text":"or increase safety measures at polling sites .","depth":11},{"id":113,"text":"That ' s a meager investment","depth":8},{"id":114,"text":"compared with the $ 2 billion","depth":9},{"id":115,"text":"that","depth":12},{"id":116,"text":"the Brennan Center for Justice recently said","depth":12},{"id":117,"text":"is needed","depth":11},{"id":118,"text":"to ensure the pandemic does not jeopardize a free and fair election .","depth":10}],"relations":[{"parent":237,"left":0,"right":236,"relation":"organization","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":236,"left":173,"right":235,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":173,"left":156,"right":172,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":156,"left":136,"right":155,"relation":"adversative","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":136,"left":123,"right":135,"relation":"context","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":123,"left":1,"right":122,"relation":"context","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":122,"left":2,"right":121,"relation":"context","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":121,"left":3,"right":120,"relation":"joint","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":120,"left":4,"right":5,"relation":"causal","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":135,"left":128,"right":134,"relation":"adversative","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":128,"left":124,"right":127,"relation":"purpose","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":124,"left":6,"right":7,"relation":"attribution","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":127,"left":8,"right":126,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":126,"left":9,"right":125,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":125,"left":10,"right":11,"relation":"mode","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":134,"left":12,"right":133,"relation":"joint","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":133,"left":129,"right":132,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":129,"left":13,"right":14,"relation":"purpose","nuclearity":"NS"},{"par